<div class="dash-grid">
  <div class="dash-card today"><b>오늘 방문</b><strong class="<%=level(S.todayViews)%>"><%=num(S.todayViews)%></strong><span class="stat-note">이번주 <%=num(S.weekViews)%> · 이번달 <%=num(S.monthViews)%></span></div>
  <div class="dash-card today"><b>오늘 가입</b><strong class="<%=level(S.todayUsers)%>"><%=num(S.todayUsers)%></strong><span class="stat-note">이번주 <%=num(S.weekUsers)%></span></div>
  <a class="dash-card today dashboard-card-link" href="#inquiries" data-panel="inquiries"><%-alertDot(S.todayInquiries)%><b>오늘 입점신청</b><strong class="<%=level(S.todayInquiries)%>"><%=num(S.todayInquiries)%></strong><span class="stat-note">일반/입점 문의</span></a>
  <a class="dash-card hot dashboard-card-link" href="#revenue" data-panel="revenue"><b>오늘 매출</b><strong><%=money(S.todayRevenue)%></strong><span class="stat-note">입금확인 완료 기준</span></a>
</div>
<div class="dash-grid">
  <a class="dash-card dashboard-card-link" href="#revenue" data-panel="revenue"><b>이번달 매출</b><strong><%=money(S.monthRevenue)%></strong></a>
  <a class="dash-card dashboard-card-link" href="#revenue" data-panel="revenue"><b>올해 매출</b><strong><%=money(S.yearRevenue)%></strong></a>
  <a class="dash-card dashboard-card-link" href="#vendors" data-panel="vendors"><b>활성 광고</b><strong class="<%=level(S.activeAds)%>"><%=num(S.activeAds)%></strong><span class="stat-note">일반/추천 노출</span></a>
  <a class="dash-card dashboard-card-link" href="#banners" data-panel="banners"><b>프리미엄 배너</b><strong class="<%=level(S.activeBanners)%>"><%=num(S.activeBanners)%></strong></a>
</div>
<div class="dash-grid">
  <a class="dash-card alert dashboard-card-link" href="#inquiries" data-panel="inquiries"><%-alertDot(S.pendingInquiries)%><b>입점 승인대기</b><strong class="<%=level(S.pendingInquiries)%>"><%=num(S.pendingInquiries)%></strong></a>
  <a class="dash-card warn dashboard-card-link" href="#vendorRequests" data-panel="vendorRequests"><%-alertDot(S.pendingVendorRequests)%><b>수정요청 대기</b><strong class="<%=level(S.pendingVendorRequests)%>"><%=num(S.pendingVendorRequests)%></strong></a>
  <a class="dash-card warn dashboard-card-link" href="#adCenter" data-panel="adCenter"><%-alertDot((S.pendingAdRequests||0)+(S.pendingBannerRequests||0))%><b>광고/배너 신청</b><strong class="<%=level((S.pendingAdRequests||0)+(S.pendingBannerRequests||0))%>"><%=num((S.pendingAdRequests||0)+(S.pendingBannerRequests||0))%></strong></a>
  <a class="dash-card alert dashboard-card-link" href="#adCenter" data-panel="adCenter"><%-alertDot(S.waitingPayments)%><b>입금확인 대기</b><strong class="<%=level(S.waitingPayments)%>"><%=num(S.waitingPayments)%></strong></a>
</div>
<div class="dash-grid">
  <a class="dash-card alert dashboard-card-link" href="#reports" data-panel="reports"><%-alertDot(S.pendingReports)%><b>신고 대기</b><strong class="<%=level(S.pendingReports)%>"><%=num(S.pendingReports)%></strong></a>
  <a class="dash-card warn dashboard-card-link" href="#vendors" data-panel="vendors"><%-alertDot(S.expiring7)%><b>7일 내 만료</b><strong class="<%=level(S.expiring7)%>"><%=num(S.expiring7)%></strong></a>
